uld be going around completely unaware that you're the one responsible for the Innocents' fall. Could you be... Insane?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/68b84023fccf434a0420f34e096a3876.poster.avif?t=1770719776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/68b84023fccf434a0420f34e096a3876.webm?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/68b84023fccf434a0420f34e096a3876.mp4?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/c38a5b9f2e1099d10ecfe4261c2e1cab.avif?t=1770719776\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either collect information and try to survive the night to uncover the impostor in the morning. Eliminate impostors using your role, and avoid suspicion at all costs. Or have your own agenda to manipulate the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/3c7bdeab3e345421e80184081b187678.poster.avif?t=1770719776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/3c7bdeab3e345421e80184081b187678.webm?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/3c7bdeab3e345421e80184081b187678.mp4?t=1770719776\"