 collected, or shifting suspicion toward someone else. The choice is yours...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/8a767d592a2402e0ea9b55bace1300c6.poster.avif?t=1770719776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/8a767d592a2402e0ea9b55bace1300c6.webm?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/8a767d592a2402e0ea9b55bace1300c6.mp4?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customizable Characters:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to stand out? Use the in-game currency, Feign Cookies, to unlock stylish costumes and accessorize your avatar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/66ed6dd292f82c48a8a84364f554848a.poster.avif?t=1770719776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/66ed6dd292f82c48a8a84364f554848a.webm?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436990/extras/66ed6dd292f82c48a8a84364f554848a.mp4?t=1770719776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
